            <title>Version 1.0.2</title>
            <sparkle:version>11</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed long recordings (30min+) failing to process</li>
                    <li>Recordings now process up to 3x faster with parallel transcription</li>
                    <li>Added estimated time remaining during processing</li>
                    <li>Improved reliability with automatic retry on network errors</li>
                    <li>Fixed summarization timeout for long meetings</li>
                    <li>Transcripts are now saved immediately — never lost if processing fails</li>
                    <li>Fixed microphone not activating on first launch</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
